              img(src="images/in_earth.png", width="400", style="margin-left:150px;")
              br
        
        h3 No projections, time series tools, or geoprocessing. Just data that works.
        div#finish_line_cont
      
      div#examples.main_cont
        h2 Examples
        div
          ol
            li
              h4(style="margin-top:-30px;") Habitat for Humanity in Bibb County, GA
              p Buildings data illustrated the impact that Habitat for Humanity has had in their neighborhood. Houses were marked green (for renovations), red (for demolitions), or orange (unchanged).
              p
                a(href="http://maconmaps.herokuapp.com/everything.html?table=lynmore&user=mapmeld&lat=32.787338&lng=-83.646888&z=17") The final map
                span &nbsp;was presented at a Code for America event at Mercer University's Center for Collaborative Journalism.
            li
              h4 Historic Chicago
              p
                span At an OpenGov Hack Night,&nbsp;
                a(href="http://historicchicago.herokuapp.com") Historic Chicago
                span &nbsp;was born. Instant timeline maps show when buildings in your neighborhood were built.
              br
